> Hi everyone.
>
> [Description]
> Instagram mobile application 168.0.0.40.355 and web application didn't verify the changed email
> address. In this case attacker can use anyone's email address as the account's linked email. This
> can cause the Identity theft.
> 
> ------------------------------------------
> 
> 
> [Vulnerability Type]
> other / privacy issue
> 
> ------------------------------------------
> 
> [Vendor of Product]
> Facebook
> 
> ------------------------------------------
> 
> [Affected Product Code Base]
> Instagram mobile application 168.0.0.40.355 and web application
> 
> ------------------------------------------
> 
> [Affected Component]
> Change Email, verifying email
> 
> ------------------------------------------
> 
> [Attack Type]
> other / Denial of service
> 
> ------------------------------------------
> 
> [Impact Information Disclosure]
> no
> 
> ------------------------------------------
> 
> [Attack Vectors]
> attacker can replace connected email address to someone's email address without verification
> 
> ------------------------------------------
> 
> [Reference]
> Instagram
